{"name": "scda-dash-auth", "metadata": {"name": "scda-dash-auth", "version": "0.2.2", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["dash-auth"], "summary": "wrapper for scda dash authentication qdt auth service and Microsoft Identity Platform", "upload_time": 1733348818}, "documentation": ["# Introduction\n\nDash authorization using Microsoft Azure Active Directory and QDT Authentication framework.\nThis projects requires the authentication service running.\n\n## Installation\n\nInstall the package using pip:\n\n```bash\npip install scda_dash_auth\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo add authentication, add the following to your Dash app:\n\n```python\nfrom scda_dash_auth import SCDAAuth\n\nauth = SCDAAuth(\n    app,\n    app_name = 'my-app',\n    secret_key = 'some-secret-key-for-session',\n    auth_url = 'http://0.0.0.0:8000',\n)\n```\n\nThis will add the authentication to your Dash app. The `auth_url` should point to the authentication service.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "scda_dash_auth", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "scda_dash_auth.SCDAAuth", "xref": {"fqname": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth", "bases": ["dash_auth.auth.Auth"], "methods": [{"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": {"name": "dash.Dash", "xref": {"fqname": "dash.Dash", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "app_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "secret_key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "auth_url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "login_route", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "logout_route", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "callback_route", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "log_signin", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "public_routes", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "logout_page", "type": {"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Response", "xref": {"fqname": "flask.Response", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "secure_session", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Secure a Dash app through SCDA/QDT Auth service.\n\nParameters\n----------\napp : dash.Dash\n    Dash app to secure\napp_name : str\n    Name of the app registered in the SCDA/QDT Auth service\nsecret_key : str\n    Secret key used to sign the session for the app\nauth_url : str\n    URL to the SCDA/QDT Auth service\nlogin_route : str, optional\n    Route to login, by default \"/login\"\nlogout_route : str, optional\n    Route to logout, by default \"/logout\"\ncallback_route : str, optional\n    Route to callback for the current service. By default \"/callback\"\nlog_signin : bool, optional\n    Log sign-ins, by default False\npublic_routes : Optional[list], optional\n    List of public routes, by default None\nlogout_page : Union[str, Response], optional\n    Page to redirect to after logout, by default None\nsecure_session : bool, optional\n    Whether to ensure the session is secure, setting the flasck config\n    SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE and SESSION_COOKIE_HTTPONLY to True,\n    by default False"]}, {"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth.is_authorized", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth.verify_token", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth.registration_request", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Response", "xref": {"fqname": "flask.Response", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "scda_dash_auth.scda_auth.SCDAAuth.login_request", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "retur